ygData.messageBody:
On Tue, 11 Jan 2000, Daniel Lloyd wrote:

> Okay simple question here what is the best way to get through level 30

Alligators in Cazic-Thule are best for 30. Quantity over quality is
important for the proverbial "hell" levels. From my experience

30: Cazic-Thule gators
35: Cazic-Thule UTR (upper throne room), Archon, that big thing
40: Solusek B pool room (4 man group, 10 hour camp, 3 bubbles exp)
Lower Guk Priest/Crusader (lots of spawns)
45: Solusek B king room (with good puller)

Athren Notechaser, 44th composition in progress
Cazic-Thule
